posts.subject: Get ready for an influx of leftists and shills
posts.body: I'm in a few leftist groups on kikebook to mole and I've been seeing this site be tossed around a good bit. A lot of them are almost afraid to come on here but I'm sure in due time we'll have this place being shit up like the rest.

I think it took me a while to actually around. I started coming on chans when I was 13 or 14 so 10 or 11 years ago. I always noticed a difference in the way how whites and blacks acted so much differently except for the few le based blacks but the more I payed attention 100% of the ones i could be around were mixed. I always knew the world was fucked and it was a divine blessing to be born an American from seeing videos from Mexico, China, Africa, etc. Apart from a few very close friends I can be myself around I'm kind of socially isolated because people STILL think 4chan is a scary place filled with CP. It's just sad at this point.

I've done my part though, I've definitely turned my gf into a racist after we moved to a 97 percent white area. The shock of seeing how nice people are to strangers and going back to the city and seeing how fucking broken the communities are was an impossibility huge redpill for her even though she doesn't admit it.

But it does take time and you don't have to be a super Chad to make it happen but you also can't be a cuck in the relationship.
